{"tid":1038844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到咁多間中學欺凌事件，我就覺得自己好好彩","createTime":"2019-02-27T04:06:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T13:36:20.000Z","uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"06bfbc938d8d25b252089ce8938fda730efeff0c","tid":1038844,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:06:35.000Z","msg":"我初中嗰陣都有被同學欺凌得好犀利<br />\n但好彩有一大班老師幫我<br />\n最後去到高中，我都可以有啲朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔似個班老師乜都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由得啲畀人欺凌嘅同學自生自滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1783b48d420dc094deca919ec5817a3db0b3984","tid":1038844,"uid":77569,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:07:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5514a0fb38de6739dd4a0aa739f12625d84a977","tid":1038844,"uid":179548,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"咪又係日日上連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89012d9aec6ecefb495d9756ea766e472f09fbda","tid":1038844,"uid":76674,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:18:15.000Z","msg":"識得有個男仔成日屌人老母，俾人除咗條褲係小童群益會打到屎忽爆哂都未識收口，有次仲唱個女仔係公廁，係人都上得，嗰次佢就甘啦"},{"pid":"9135413d68945c3bc40a53524b3bd82989664027","tid":1038844,"uid":141869,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T04:19:31.000Z","msg":"咁你覺得被欺凌既人,<br />\n純粹係唔好彩畀人揀中左,<br />\n定佢地本身多多少少有啲問題?"},{"pid":"008bcd80cae209a8b7ef1abe9775961f66806231","tid":1038844,"uid":207352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9135413d68945c3bc40a53524b3bd82989664027","tid":1038844,"uid":141869,"like":1,"dislike":3,"sco